data.description: This wide-open floor plan ranch has the ideal kid and pet-friendly backyard. With a 6 ft fence and surrounding trees and nature, this gives you an ideal amount of privacy and no neighbors to the south or west. This house boasts several updates including hard floors, fresh paint in every room throughout the main floor and basement, and roof just over three years old. Oversized primary bedroom with sitting area and two closets, one being a walk-in. A convenient walkout basement has engineered hard floors in the main family area and bedrooms. The basement's large bedroom has large closet space to match.  Also, there's a workout/office room and a basement bathroom. In the Millard school district with a nice playground just one block away, this is your perfect family home.
